This file contains the learning goals that we expect the children to understand and assimilate

Science is open
  All methods, figures, measurements and figures must be public and revisable by others
  
  It will be reinforced by the fact that experiments and their data will be accessible by everyone
  
Science is methodological
  Science follows a well stablished and defined method, the scientific method. All steps should be followed in the right order.
  
  It will be reinforced by the flow of the experiment in the application, it won't be possible to move to a step unless the previous ones have been completed.
